    <h1>First-principles strategy for defense innovation, AI, and national resilience.</h1>
    <p class="sub">Strategy is choosing what not to do. For two decades I've helped governments and investors turn deep expertise into the few decisions that create advantage — in the field, not the seminar room.</p>
